# VisionIntuition #
#####*An App of understanding you!*#####
##1.Introduction##
  The main function of the software is automatic image content recognition, and automatically adding text description. The following features are also integrated: **face matching**, **age testing**, **text recognition**, **sharing and store**.
####Automatic Identification+####
  A picture through the user input, the first system of feature extraction, image content into the text feature, again in the text of the second feature extraction, i.e., the extraction of key features. The system according to the key features to match the text description.
####Face Matching####
  User input two containing pictures of frontal face, through feature extraction and match to determine whether to belong to the same person, you can also output of similarity.
####Age Test####
  The user inputs a face picture, the system estimated the age and gender characteristics by character.
####Character Recognition####
Through optical character recognition algorithm to identify the user input images with text, which will pictures of characters into the character.

To share and save the text to maps or caption and image fusion, the user can select the save to local or shared to social networks.
